"{\"uid\": \"hindustantimes.com-trending-kolkata-doctor-watched-neeraj-chopras-olympics-final-with-friends-before-she-was-raped-murdered-101723523056317.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Subscribe Now!\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 14, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Get features like  The young doctor who was raped and murdered in Kolkata last week watched the Paris Olympics 2024 late at night at a state-run medical college and hospital in the city, shortly before the crime took place.\", \"from\": 15, \"to\": 238, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 81, \"end\": 88, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kolkata\", \"score\": 0.9999996036884443, \"rank\": 3.0875836317912816e-07, \"text\": \"Kolkata\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kolkata\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kolkata\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her semi-naked body was found in a seminar hall at RG Kar Medical College and Hospital on Friday morning, and a civic volunteer was arrested on Saturday in connection with the crime.\", \"from\": 239, \"to\": 421, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The victim, who was on-call duty, along with four other colleagues had ordered dinner which they ate at the seminar room around 12:30 am.\", \"from\": 423, \"to\": 561, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They also watched the Olympics.\", \"from\": 562, \"to\": 593, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After they left, she retired to bed in the seminar room,\\\" said an officer.\", \"from\": 594, \"to\": 668, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The postgraduate trainee doctor reportedly watched javelin star Neeraj Chopra's Paris Olympics 2024 final at the institute.\", \"from\": 670, \"to\": 793, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 734, \"end\": 747, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Neeraj_Chopra\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Neeraj Chopra\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Neeraj_Chopra\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Neeraj_Chopra\"}, {\"begin\": 750, \"end\": 764, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A 33-year-old man called Sanjoy Roy was arrested in the rape and murder of the doctor inKolkata.\", \"from\": 795, \"to\": 891, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 820, \"end\": 826, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sanjoy\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sanjoy\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sanjoy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sanjoy\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He had joined Kolkata Police as a civic volunteer in 2019, was married at least four times and known as a \\\"womaniser\\\", the police said.\", \"from\": 892, \"to\": 1027, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 906, \"end\": 920, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kolkata_Police\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kolkata Police\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kolkata_Police\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kolkata_Police\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"During the investigation, it was found that he had a history of physically abusing his wives, an officer said.\", \"from\": 1029, \"to\": 1139, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Roy was allegedly addicted to pornography and his mobile phone had several such contents, police said on Monday.\", \"from\": 1141, \"to\": 1253, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The pornography content in his mobile phone was quite disturbing and violent.\", \"from\": 1255, \"to\": 1333, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We wonder about the state of his mind as watching such things is quite unnatural,\\\" the officer said.\", \"from\": 1334, \"to\": 1434, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The crime triggered a massive strike by resident doctorsin government hospitals across the country as they went on an indefinite strike on Monday.\", \"from\": 1436, \"to\": 1582, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"West Bengal Chief MinisterMamata Banerjeepledged to transfer the case to the CBI (Central Bureau of Investigation) if the state police fails to solve it by Sunday.\", \"from\": 1584, \"to\": 1747, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1661, \"end\": 1664, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Central_Bureau_of_Investigation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.267568382764993e-23, \"text\": \"CBI\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Central_Bureau_of_Investigation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Central_Bureau_of_Investigation\"}]}]}"